== MyLibrary

This is a minimalist Ebook library written in Ruby on Rails.

(c)2009 Patrick Morgan
http://www.patrick-morgan.net/

== Setup
 $ git clone git://github.com/codeprimate/mylibrary.git
 $ cd mylibrary
 $ git submodule init
 $ git submodule update
 $ cp config/database.yml.example config/database.yml
 $ cp config/application.yml.example config/application.yml
 $ cp config/amazon_s3.yml.example config/amazon_s3.yml

Configure your yml files.

 $ rake db:create:all
 $ script/server

Go to http://admin:spartacus@localhost:3000/users/new to create a user account.
Guests may view the ebook list at http://guest:knowledge@localhsot:3000/

Passwords are configurable in config/application.yml

-
EOF